{
  "name": "RPlog_Back_in_the_Good_Ole_New_Republic",
  "title": "Back in the Good Ole New Republic",
  "summary": "Returning to Corellia's Coronet City spaceport, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios, her companion the mechanic Orson Tighe, and the wary Selas Simon land discreetly, mindful of the dangers their last visit brought. As they disembark, they discuss caution, the Sith device afflicting Eva Sargent and Cort Stasus, and Jessalyn's intent to contact Princess Leia and the New Republic. Simon, knowing he is distrusted, opts to keep his distance from any meeting and tend his own ship. Their plans are interrupted when Rislyn, a young woman secretly assigned by NR Intelligence to find Jessalyn, recognizes her at the starport. Dropping her teenage facade, Rislyn quietly reveals her mission and the troubling news that Luke is still missing and Karrde is in trouble with the Empire. As Orson and Simon depart on their own errands, Jessalyn asks Rislyn to help arrange an audience with Councilor Organa-Solo aboard the Chancellor, only to be struck mid-conversation by a terrifying Force vision of swirling Darkness, leaving her shaken and pale.",
